snippet.title: KPOP Demon Hunters Bloxburg RP with Baby Goldie
snippet.description:
Titi Games & Goldie play bloxburg. Today is a very special day for my daughter Goldie! She’s a huge fan of the viral show K-Pop Demon Hunters and knows all the songs and dances by heart. To surprise her, I take her to McDonald’s to grab the brand-new K-Pop Happy Meal—and the look on her face is priceless!

But that’s not all… inside Roblox, Goldie gets the ultimate surprise—she actually meets her idols, the Huntrix girls: Rumi, Zoey, and Jinu! 

Join us for laughs, music, and the sweetest dad-and-daughter adventure ever. This video is full of Roblox fun, happy meals, and K-Pop magic you won’t want to miss!

#roblox #kpopdemonhunters #bloxburgfamilyrp
